Titolo: Bomberman Story DS

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Bomberman Story DS (ボンバーマンストーリーDS) is a puzzle action role-playing video game for the Nintendo DS. It was announced at the Nintendo Conference 2005. It is able to connect to the Nintendo Wi-Fi connection service. This game has received translations into several languages including English for releases in Europe and Australia by Rising Star Games.